title: E.ON tests inductive charging for electric vehicles in and around Berlin (EON SE)
text: ( Source : EON SE) E.ON and three partner organizations are conducting field trials of wireless, inductive charging for electric vehicles (EVs). The project is supported by the German Federal Ministry for the Environment , Nature Conservation ,
